@page
@model MyAspNetApp.Pages.AboutModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}
<h1>@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<p>We are a group of four enthusiastic students from Kocaeli University, dedicated to creating innovative web applications. This project is a part of our coursework for the Web Programming course, where we aim to develop a functional and user-friendly shoe sales website. Our mission is to leverage the skills and knowledge we've acquired during our studies to build a platform that meets the needs of our users while providing an exceptional shopping experience.</p>

<h2>Our Journey</h2>
<p>Our journey began with a shared passion for technology and a desire to create impactful web applications. Throughout our studies, we have worked on various projects, but this shoe sales website represents a culmination of our learning and teamwork. We have spent countless hours brainstorming, coding, and testing to ensure that our site not only functions well but also provides a seamless user experience.</p>

<h2>Project Goals</h2>
<p>The primary goal of our project is to create an intuitive and engaging platform where users can browse and purchase shoes with ease. We have focused on implementing features that enhance the user experience, such as a dynamic cart system, user authentication, and responsive design. By combining these elements, we aim to deliver a site that is both visually appealing and highly functional.</p>

<h2>Meet Our Team</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Ebru:</strong> Lead Developer - Ebru is responsible for overseeing the entire development process, ensuring that all components work together seamlessly.</li>
    <li><strong>Emir:</strong> Frontend Developer - Emir focuses on creating a user-friendly interface, making sure that the design is both attractive and easy to navigate.</li>
    <li><strong>Zehra:</strong> Backend Developer - Zehra handles the server-side logic, managing the database interactions and ensuring the site runs smoothly.</li>
    <li><strong>Süheyla:</strong> Database Administrator - Süheyla is in charge of maintaining the database, ensuring data integrity and security.</li>
</ul>

<h2>Our Vision</h2>
<p>We envision a platform that not only meets the current needs of our users but also has the potential to grow and adapt to future demands. We are committed to continuous improvement and innovation, always seeking ways to enhance the functionality and user experience of our site. Our long-term goal is to expand our project, incorporating new features and technologies as we learn and evolve in our field.</p>

<h2>Thank You</h2>
<p>We want to take this opportunity to thank our professors and peers at Kocaeli University for their support and guidance throughout this project. Their insights and feedback have been invaluable in helping us reach our goals.</p>

<p>We hope you enjoy using our website as much as we enjoyed developing it. Your feedback is important to us, so please do not hesitate to share your thoughts and suggestions. Together, we can continue to improve and deliver a platform that truly serves your needs.</p>
